Instructions for how to build and run vcnc-server may be found at
https://nicko7i.github.io/vcnc/developer/building/vcnc-server-build.html

You can also read the source code at *project-dir*/documentation/developer/building/vcnc-server-build.rst

**spoiler alert**:

```
../configure --with-pic --with-toolroot=/opt/frqu/TOOLROOT
```

Do not delete this file, it is required to keep autotools happy.
